{"id": "ChIJvSRHIya5woARP_Vr_vFHnT4", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 2547, "displayName": {"text": "Sun Nong Dan", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJvSRHIya5woARP_Vr_vFHnT4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RMVJUQk5jR3BoVEcxa1VHMWtNRGh2ZERWT1NuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Personally, I think the food is good, but not \"we should wait in line for an hour or more\" good. We came here the night before and it was packed with a line extended around the parking.  The next day we came during 2pm and it was about 50% capacity. We ordered the Galbi Jjim, which is pretty popular and representative for this joint. The flavor was balanced and the Galbi was tender and there was a good amount of it, the tteokbokki was perfectly cooked, soft chew, not the cheap powder type that breaks.  The M portion is definitely enough for 2 people, but for $100?  I didn't really find the value here, then again, you don't have 4 locations if you aren't making a killing on the margin.  I just don't see any wow factor for the $100.  Overall, it is just another overblown social media trap. But overall the food is pretty good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Personally, I think the food is good, but not \"we should wait in line for an hour or more\" good. We came here the night before and it was packed with a line extended around the parking.  The next day we came during 2pm and it was about 50% capacity. We ordered the Galbi Jjim, which is pretty popular and representative for this joint. The flavor was balanced and the Galbi was tender and there was a good amount of it, the tteokbokki was perfectly cooked, soft chew, not the cheap powder type that breaks.  The M portion is definitely enough for 2 people, but for $100?  I didn't really find the value here, then again, you don't have 4 locations if you aren't making a killing on the margin.  I just don't see any wow factor for the $100.  Overall, it is just another overblown social media trap. But overall the food is pretty good.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "D “Juanito” H", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114187871045557704407/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs2s36bUMcAC_b7B8HWG0u2Bt53YVpCE_4PnijIscU7bsLtVGd=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T17:13:51.197552717Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RMVJUQk5jR3BoVEcxa1VHMWtNRGh2ZERWT1NuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21RMVJUQk5jR3BoVEcxa1VHMWtNRGh2ZERWT1NuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b926234724bd:0x3e9d47f1fe6bf53f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvSRHIya5woARP_Vr_vFHnT4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s4NGMyWk5aVzFSYjJkTldtTjZSRkZhWVRVM1RVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Excellent restaurant for Korean soups and stews. The banchan are flavorful and addicting, especially the buchoo or chives kimchi.\n\nReviewers complaining about price are ignorant of the extremely generous breakfast special? This restaurant has nourished me many times over the years with their breakfast special and complimentary hot tea. It feels generous and like the restaurant is giving back to the community.\n\nService is great, though especially so from Jayden and Brian, whom I’m always glad to see during the day shifts. They’re always kind and patient and attentive, even when the restaurant is very busy as it is often.\n\nThe soups themselves are flavorful and taste good quality. The tta roh guk bap is especially seasoned and delicious. The rice is always good too.\n\nThis morning I got the traditional seolangtang whose calming plainness balances very well with the seasoned banchan.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Excellent restaurant for Korean soups and stews. The banchan are flavorful and addicting, especially the buchoo or chives kimchi.\n\nReviewers complaining about price are ignorant of the extremely generous breakfast special? This restaurant has nourished me many times over the years with their breakfast special and complimentary hot tea. It feels generous and like the restaurant is giving back to the community.\n\nService is great, though especially so from Jayden and Brian, whom I’m always glad to see during the day shifts. They’re always kind and patient and attentive, even when the restaurant is very busy as it is often.\n\nThe soups themselves are flavorful and taste good quality. The tta roh guk bap is especially seasoned and delicious. The rice is always good too.\n\nThis morning I got the traditional seolangtang whose calming plainness balances very well with the seasoned banchan.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Evan Yu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101566331211968028063/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4_LR4oa7B72pb9Kep_Uh5ldSdaxEg1XUfXBLe8MB5TeTpNQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-10T21:58:00.205000581Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s4NGMyWk5aVzFSYjJkTldtTjZSRkZhWVRVM1RVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s4NGMyWk5aVzFSYjJkTldtTjZSRkZhWVRVM1RVRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b926234724bd:0x3e9d47f1fe6bf53f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvSRHIya5woARP_Vr_vFHnT4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201VlRtSnVNSEZYZFdGQ09GRjZValpJZVhKemRrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We really enjoyed our visit to Sun Nong Dan. The food was delicious, flavorful, and definitely worth trying. The portions were generous, and the atmosphere inside was lively and enjoyable. The only downside was that we had to wait quite a long time to get in, but once we were seated, the experience was much better. Overall, we had a good time and would come back again — just recommend planning for a wait during busy hours.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We really enjoyed our visit to Sun Nong Dan. The food was delicious, flavorful, and definitely worth trying. The portions were generous, and the atmosphere inside was lively and enjoyable. The only downside was that we had to wait quite a long time to get in, but once we were seated, the experience was much better. Overall, we had a good time and would come back again — just recommend planning for a wait during busy hours.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ayaulym Tokina", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104216473938431524991/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUu0aJerrp8XbSyxiD38JbNmYbS-QMH1KWJ8sdISbL26gi187E=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-24T23:45:52.623351056Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201VlRtSnVNSEZYZFdGQ09GRjZValpJZVhKemRrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201VlRtSnVNSEZYZFdGQ09GRjZValpJZVhKemRrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b926234724bd:0x3e9d47f1fe6bf53f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvSRHIya5woARP_Vr_vFHnT4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKbE5ETTRlVkUzYm1aTmRreFJWblZGTlhkUWVsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "2nd time here and got the same dish. It’s a bit rowdy inside, because it can get pretty busy. I’ve gone dinner time both times. Food is pretty fresh and tasty and the large option is definitely enough for at least 4-5 people. The flambé experience is fun and the cheese pull is peak.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "2nd time here and got the same dish. It’s a bit rowdy inside, because it can get pretty busy. I’ve gone dinner time both times. Food is pretty fresh and tasty and the large option is definitely enough for at least 4-5 people. The flambé experience is fun and the cheese pull is peak.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "French", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110207552237963061407/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVe7CL-zAoqtUaVn4saSn9ypifITK8TBPngW1gq8Vv7g_ZBbTg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-03T07:31:13.676801Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKbE5ETTRlVkUzYm1aTmRreFJWblZGTlhkUWVsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKbE5ETTRlVkUzYm1aTmRreFJWblZGTlhkUWVsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b926234724bd:0x3e9d47f1fe6bf53f"}, {"name": "places/ChIJvSRHIya5woARP_Vr_vFHnT4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GUFIxWXlZalV5U1dnemIwUndaRE55VDFFNFQxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Galbi Tang - $23.99 - this is like the Mexican soup, cocido de res.\nKoh Galbi Jjim - $119.99 for Large\nAdd cheese - $8\nAdd rice cake - $6\n\nKoh Galbi Jjim is a huge dish of braised beef short ribs, back rib, and oxtail plus delicious cheese and rice cakes and all of the complimentary banchan. You can choose your spice level. It's enough to feed 4-5 people, easily.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Galbi Tang - $23.99 - this is like the Mexican soup, cocido de res.\nKoh Galbi Jjim - $119.99 for Large\nAdd cheese - $8\nAdd rice cake - $6\n\nKoh Galbi Jjim is a huge dish of braised beef short ribs, back rib, and oxtail plus delicious cheese and rice cakes and all of the complimentary banchan. You can choose your spice level. It's enough to feed 4-5 people, easily.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "avey", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contri